The showcase format in this mockup emphasizes clarity over spectacle. Visitors should understand what was built, who it was built for, and what questions remain open.

Projects included assistive reading tools, campus analytics dashboards, and lightweight data workflows for community services. The content is intentionally anonymized, but the editorial structure mirrors the kind of stories a real institution would surface.
